=== FW 1.4 ===
* Increased shutdown timeout to 31 minutes when remote is locked.
* Only right button can be used for starting.

=== FW 1.3 ===
* Upgraded to zephyr 2.4.99.
* Ignore first button click at start.

=== FW 1.2 ===
* Enable control during intro screen.
* Show firmware version in temperature screen.

=== FW 1.1 ===
* Handle handle_esb_rx in thread to avoid using float in an interrupt, as that is not allowed.
* Added imperial unit support.
* Added NVM storage for settings.
* Safe joystick sampling.

=== FW 1.0 ===
* First release.

